<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>참가 인원 수 확인</title>
</head>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.12.4.js"></script>
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.js"></script>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//code.jquery.com/ui/1.12.1/themes/base/jquery-ui.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
<body style="margin-left: 20px; padding-top: 40px">
<h2></h2>
<h2> 총 {{total}} 명 신청하였습니다.</h2>
<h2></h2>
<input style="text-align: center" type="text" id="datepicker" value="{{date}}"> 이후의 날짜만 검색합니다.
<input type="hidden" name="host" id="host" value="{{host}}">
<br/>
<br/>
<table class="table table-horizontal table-bordered">
    <tbody>
    {{#counters}}
        <tr>
            <td style="text-align: center">{{id}}</td>
            <td>{{created}}</td>
        </tr>
    {{/counters}}
    </tbody>
</table>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function () {
        $("#datepicker").datepicker({
            dateFormat: 'yy-mm-dd',
            showMonthAfterYear: true
        });
        $("#datepicker").change(function () {
            var host = $("#host").val();
            var date = this.value;
            var url = window.location.origin + window.location.pathname;
            window.location.replace(url + "?host=" + host + "&date=" + date);
        })
    })
</script>
</body>

</html>
